    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-05-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-06-17T14:42:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sending Outside Support Act of 2020 or the SOS Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services&nbsp;to distribute funds to allow states to establish strike teams that may be deployed to skilled nursing facilities and nursing facilities with cases of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) to help with clinical care, infection control, or staffing. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>SOS Act of 2020</title>
